resources.string: Social Tees Animal Rescue is a non-profit 501c3 no kill rescue in NYC /n finding forever homes for abandoned dogs and cats. We are a foster-based, /n community oriented organization founded on the principles of /n responsible pet ownership and creating a supportive environment for our staff and volunteers. /n Ensuring access to thorough veterinary treatment and the wellbeing of our animals are our highest priorities, /n and we pride ourselves in matching each animal with the family best able to meet its needs for life.
